This program is a repetition bot in telegram and VKontakte services.

Use with default parameters - ./bot or bot (with Path in command line).
Use with other parameters   - run with command line arguments:
-h or --help - this message
-s tel or --service=telegramm - service Telegramm (default)
-s vc or --service=vkontakte - service Vcontakte
(You can choose only one of these services.You can run two instances of
the program with different services).
-r n or --repeat=n n={1..5} - number repeat (defaut value=3)
-l v v={d,i,w,e} or --loglevel v v={debug,info,warning,error},
defaul value=info.

Quantity and order of entering command line arguments is unimportant.
The default settings are located in the corresponding files in this
directory (JSON). In these files, you can change only the number of
repetitions, the logging level and the help information output by the bot,
if you change the names and tokens, the program's performance will be disrupted.

Examples usage:
./bot
./bot --help
./bot -s vc --loglevel=error
./bot --service=telegramm -r 2 -l d

